# Compiled tool binaries.
# Each tool builds to jek_<tool>/jek<tool> with no extension (e.g. jek_wc/jekwc).
# Ignore those binaries, but keep all source, headers, and shell scripts.
# This needs no edits when you add a new tool, as long as it follows the
# jek_<tool>/jek<tool> naming convention.
jek_*/jek*
!jek_*/*.c
!jek_*/*.h
!jek_*/*.sh

# Stale artifacts from ad-hoc `gcc -o main` / `gcc -o test` during development.
jek_*/main
jek_*/test
